Package: fairml
Type: Package
Title: Fair Models in Machine Learning
Version: 0.3
Date: 2020-09-09
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: methods, optiSolve
Suggests: lattice
Author: Marco Scutari [aut, cre]
